{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/libgdx/libgdx/issues/6285","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/libgdx/libgdx","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/libgdx/libgdx/issues/6285/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/libgdx/libgdx/issues/6285/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/libgdx/libgdx/issues/6285/events","html_url":"https://github.com/libgdx/libgdx/issues/6285","id":750037426,"node_id":"MDU6SXNzdWU3NTAwMzc0MjY=","number":6285,"title":"`IntMap.containsValue()` returns true for values that have been removed.","user":{"login":"nickswebsite","id":7522772,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjc1MjI3NzI=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/7522772?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/nickswebsite","html_url":"https://github.com/nickswebsite","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/nickswebsite/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/nickswebsite/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/nickswebsite/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/nickswebsite/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/nickswebsite/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/nickswebsite/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/nickswebsite/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/nickswebsite/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/nickswebsite/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"labels":[],"state":"closed","locked":false,"assignee":null,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":6,"created_at":"2020-11-24T20:32:58Z","updated_at":"2020-12-02T08:40:33Z","closed_at":"2020-11-25T17:16:37Z","author_association":"NONE","type":null,"active_lock_reason":null,"sub_issues_summary":{"total":0,"completed":0,"percent_completed":0},"issue_dependencies_summary":{"blocked_by":0,"total_blocked_by":0,"blocking":0,"total_blocking":0},"body":"`IntMap.containsValue()` returns true for stale values. This creates problems with the Gwt backend on touch screens when trying to determine if a touch identifier has been seen before as it thinks that there are multiple touches on the screen. This causes the pinch handlers to be called rather than the pan handler.\r\n\r\n#### Reproduction steps/code\r\n\r\n* Add an item to an `IntMap<>`.\r\n* Remove the item.\r\n* Call `containsValue()` with the value.\r\n* `containsValue()` returns true.\r\n\r\n#### Version of LibGDX and/or relevant dependencies\r\n_Please provide the version(s) affected._\r\n\r\n1.9.12\r\n\r\n#### Test Case\r\nThe following test fails:\r\n\r\n```java\r\nclass IntMapTest {\r\n    @Test\r\n    void test_contains_value_returns_false_after_removal() {\r\n        IntMap< Integer > map = new IntMap<>();\r\n        Integer value = 123;\r\n        map.put( 1, value );\r\n        map.remove( 1 );\r\n\r\n        assertFalse( map.containsValue( value, false ) );\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### Please select the affected platforms\r\n- [ ] Android\r\n- [ ] iOS\r\n- [x] HTML/GWT\r\n- [ ] Windows\r\n- [ ] Linux\r\n- [ ] MacOS\r\n","closed_by":{"login":"Tom-Ski","id":4346114,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjQzNDYxMTQ=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/4346114?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/Tom-Ski","html_url":"https://github.com/Tom-Ski","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Tom-Ski/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Tom-Ski/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Tom-Ski/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Tom-Ski/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Tom-Ski/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Tom-Ski/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Tom-Ski/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Tom-Ski/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://ap